If clickbait sites are to be believed, society as a whole is suffering from a bit of "superhero fatigue", but does the concept actually exist? Is Blue Beetle the cure for what has been ailing WB's when it comes to crafting a well-made origin story? Will we ever get a live-action Spider-Ham movie? Some of these questions will be answered in this episode but if you wanna know which ones, you'll have to listen! If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

